@startuml
skinparam componentStyle uml2
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title Keepit Bestellprozess - Übersicht

' === SYNCHRONER FLOW (Order-Erstellung) ===
package "Synchron: Order erstellen" {
    [Frontend] as GUI
    [POST /api/orders] as API
    [OrderController] as Ctrl
    [PostgreSQL] as DB
}

GUI --> API : Artikel-Array
API --> Ctrl : erstellt Order
Ctrl --> DB : Transaction:\n- Order\n- OrderPositions\n- DocumentJobs\n- Cart löschen

' === ASYNCHRONER FLOW (Document Generation) ===
package "Asynchron: Dokumente generieren" {
    [BullMQ Queue\n(Redis)] as Queue
    [Worker Process] as Worker
    [PDF Generator\n(Puppeteer)] as Generator
}

DB -.-> Queue : DocumentJobs\nqueue.add()
Queue --> Worker : pollt
Worker --> Generator : startet
Generator --> DB : speichert Status

note right of Queue
  Job-Typen:
  - invoice
  - license
  Status: pending→processing→completed
end note

@enduml